review_text: Sebelumnya mohon maaf, sore tadi ibu saya naik primajasa jurusan tasik jakarta lebak bulus kelas ekonomi,keberangkatan jam 3sore dari terminal indhiang  tujuan cileunyi tertera di tiket  25000 tapi kenapa ibu di tarif 75000 ,krn heran ibu sy protes tp apa yg terjadi si kondektur malah ngancem mau nurunin ibusy  di jln, sungguh tragis ibu sy bawa uang cuma 75000 sdgkn perjalanan msh akan berlanjut dg naik bus kota,krn ketiadaan uag ibu sy sampai ngemis, tp alhamdulilah sampai di rumah.sesampainya di rmh ibu sy menceritakan semua kejadian tsb. Sungguh pelayanan yg buruk, dan untuk aparat terkait sy mohon pengusutanya dampai tuntas, krn sy pelanggan setia primajasa dan krn kejadian ini sy kecewa, dan apabila tdk ada pengusutan sy akan sangat kecewa, terimakasih
review_translated_text: First of all, Im sorry, this afternoon my mother took the Primajasa route to Tasik Jakarta, Lebak Bulus, economy class, the departure was at 3pm from the Indhiang terminal, the destination Cileunyi was stated on the ticket as 25,000, but why did you get a fare of 75,000, because I was surprised that my mother protested, but what happened was the conductor was even worried. I wanted to drop my mother off on the street, it was really tragic that my mother only brought 75,000 in cash, but the journey would continue by taking a city bus, because of the lack of money, my mother had to beg, but thank God I arrived home. When I got home, my mother told me all about the incident. Really bad service, and to the relevant authorities I ask that the investigation be completed, because I am a loyal customer of Primajasa and because of this incident I am disappointed, and if there is no investigation I will be very disappointed, thank you
